Revision history for Net-BART

0.01  2026-04-06
    - Initial release
    - Net::BART: pure Perl implementation of BART (Balanced Routing Tables)
    - Net::BART::XS: C/XS implementation for maximum performance
    - IPv4 and IPv6 support
    - Operations: insert, delete, lookup (LPM), get (exact match), contains, walk
